profile:
Garage Life specializes in garage flooring, epoxy, garage doors, garage door repair, imprinted concrete driveways, driveway sealing and paving, garage storage, garage cabinets and garage packages.

Garage Doors
The reliability of your garage door will help you stay on schedule in the morning. Its beauty will greet you at the end a day. Garage Life is here to help you install and repair garage doors. You have over 600 overhead doors to choose from our catalogue, varying by material, colours and designs. Our technicians are trained and experienced, offering quality garage door repair service and installations.

Garage Door Repair & Garage Door Spring Replacement
Overhead garage doors are taken for granted until something goes wrong. As one of the top level garage door repair companies, Garage Life is here to fix your broken door and help you move on with the rest of your day.

Garage Life garage door services provide:
- Trained and experienced garage door service technicians
- Highest quality parts
- 24 / 7 emergency service
- Same day service
- First visit repair

Repair services also include: garage door spring repair and garage door spring replacement.

Garage Door Installation
Garage Life will send an overhead garage door technician to measure your garage door opening. Based on the type of door you have selected, will then give you a price.

When you choose our garage door company you'll get:
- Guidance in choosing garage door and garage door opener from a wide range of premium quality options.
- Installation by trained and experienced garage door professionals.

Our overhead door installations have been proven durable and long lasting.

You can select from a range of garage doors including: aluminum garage doors, steel doors, wood design doors, traditional carriage house doors, custom crafted wooden garage doors, fibreglass doors and more. Here are the brands that Garage Life installs and fixes: Garaga, Windsor, Amarr, Chamberlain, Clopay, Craftsman, Steelcraft, Stanley, Liftmaster, Wayne Dalton, Carriage, Lynx, Northwest Doors, Genie.
Garage Door Openers

Garage Life offers a broad selection of garage door openers with various performance, features, and durability. The garage door opener brands carried offer the ultimate in safety and security features, and are available with a variety of power levels and drive systems for all types of homes and applications, including those with rooms over the garage or those with heavy doors, as well as a series of openers that require little maintenance. We offer garage door opener installation together with the product.
Garage Door Parts

We are stocked with a plethora of various garage door openers, garage door springs, garage door parts, gate openers, gate operator parts, garage door remotes, and access control openers, overhead door keypad and systems. We also carry OEM parts and replacements including remote transmitters, receivers, openers and accessories.

Garage Door Repair and Installation Toronto
Garage Life offers garage doors, garage door openers, garage door opener remote and motors -automation â€“ spare parts and accessories online at vastly reduced prices in Toronto area. In fact we offer some of the cheapest garage doors Toronto.

Give us a call today for a quote.
